      "23": "kai oi hmiseis fulhs manassh katwkhsan en th gh apo basan ews baalermwn kai sanir kai oros aermwn kai en tw libanw autoi epleonasqhsan",
      "24": "kai outoi archgoi oikou patriwn autwn ofer kai isei kai elihl kai esdrihl kai iermia kai wdouia kai iedihl andres iscuroi dunamei andres onomastoi arcontes twn oikwn patriwn autwn",
      "25": "kai hqethsan en qew paterwn autwn kai eporneusan opisw qewn lawn ths ghs ous exhren o qeos apo proswpou autwn",
      "26": "kai ephgeiren o qeos israhl to pneuma falwc basilews assour kai to pneuma qaglaqfalnasar basilews assour kai metwkisen ton roubhn kai ton gaddi kai to hmisu fulhs manassh kai hgagen autous eis calac kai cabwr kai epi potamon gwzan ews ths hmeras tauths"
